name: Adolf Hipster.
description:
Single colour print tee, printed onto high quality Gildan t-shirts.

100% cotton pre-shrunk jersey. Seamless collar. Double needle topstitched neckline. Taped neck and shoulders. Double stitched sleeve and waist hem. Quarter-turned body to eliminate centre crease.

Size Chest (to fit) 
S - 34/36" M - 38/40" L - 42/44" XL - 46/48"

Printed on Gildan Heavy. 
100% Cotton.
